<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>Mont-Saint-Michel Guides: Tickets, Tides, History &amp; How to Visit | TouringBee</title>
<meta name="description" content="All our Mont-Saint-Michel guides in one place — abbey tickets, opening hours, the tides, how to get there, history and the best time to visit.">
<link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" sizes="any">
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon-32.png">
<link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/favicon-180.png">
<link rel="canonical" href="https://montsaintmichelguide.com/guides/">
<style>
:root{--ink:#16202a;--muted:#5c6b78;--line:#e4ebf0;--brand:#2d9cdf;--brand-d:#15688f;--bg:#fff;--soft:#f2f8fc}
*{box-sizing:border-box}
body{margin:0;font:17px/1.65 -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:var(--ink);background:var(--bg)}
.wrap{max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 20px}
img{max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block}
a{color:var(--brand-d)}
header.top{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:20;background:rgba(255,255,255,.95);backdrop-filter:blur(6px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
.topbar{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:56px}
.brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;text-decoration:none}
.brand img{width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:50%}
.brand .bt{color:var(--ink);font-weight:800;font-size:18px}
.brand .g{color:var(--brand)}
.nav-wrap{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px}
.lang{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted)}
.lang a{color:var(--muted);text-decoration:none;margin:0 3px;padding:6px 4px;display:inline-block}
.lang a.on{color:var(--ink);font-weight:700}
.ghead{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2d9cdf,#1f81bd);color:#fff;padding:48px 20px}
.ghead .wrap{max-width:820px}
.ghead h1{font-size:32px;margin:0 0 10px}
.ghead p{font-size:18px;color:#eaf6ff;margin:0;max-width:60ch}
.crumbs{font-size:13px;color:#dfeaf2;margin:0 0 12px}
.crumbs a{color:#dfeaf2;text-decoration:none}
main{padding:40px 0 60px}
.gcat{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;color:var(--muted);margin:28px 0 10px}
.gcards{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(280px,1fr));gap:18px}
.gcard{border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;background:#fff;box-shadow:0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,.06);display:flex;flex-direction:column;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;transition:box-shadow .15s,transform .15s}
.gcard:hover{box-shadow:0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.12);transform:translateY(-2px)}
.gcard img{width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/10;object-fit:cover}
.gcard .b{padding:15px 17px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;flex:1}
.gcard h3{margin:0 0 5px;font-size:18px}
.gcard p{margin:0;font-size:14px;color:var(--muted)}
.gcard.soon{opacity:.62;pointer-events:none}
.gcard.soon .tag{display:inline-block;margin-top:8px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;color:var(--brand-d);background:var(--soft);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:20px;padding:2px 9px}
footer{background:#fff;color:var(--muted);font-size:14px;padding:36px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--line);margin-top:20px}
.fbrand{font-weight:800;font-size:18px;color:var(--ink)}.fbrand span{color:var(--brand)}
@media(max-width:640px){.topbar{height:auto;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;padding:8px 0}.ghead h1{font-size:26px}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header class="top"><div class="wrap topbar">
<a class="brand" href="/"><img src="/img/logo.webp" width="30" height="30" alt="Mont-Saint-Michel Guide logo"><span class="bt">Mont-Saint-Michel<span class="g">Guide</span></span></a>
<div class="nav-wrap">
<nav class="lang"><a href="/">EN</a><a href="/fr/">FR</a><a href="/de/">DE</a><a href="/es/">ES</a><a href="/it/">IT</a><a href="/pt/">PT</a><a href="/pl/">PL</a><a href="/ru/">RU</a></nav>
</div>
</div></header>

<div class="ghead"><div class="wrap">
<nav class="crumbs"><a href="/">Home</a> &rsaquo; Guides</nav>
<h1>Mont-Saint-Michel Guides</h1>
<p>Everything you need to plan the visit — tickets, tides, history and how to get there. New guides added regularly.</p>
</div></div>

<main><div class="wrap">
<div class="gcat">Planning &amp; tickets</div>
<div class="gcards">
<a class="gcard" href="/mont-saint-michel-abbey-tickets/">
<img src="/img/abbey-800.webp" alt="Mont-Saint-Michel abbey" loading="lazy">
<div class="b"><h3>Abbey Tickets: Prices, Hours &amp; What's Inside</h3><p>2026 prices, opening hours, where to buy, and a room-by-room walk through the abbey.</p></div>
</a>
<span class="gcard soon"><img src="/img/hero-600.webp" alt="Mont-Saint-Michel across the bay" loading="lazy"><div class="b"><h3>Best Time to Visit</h3><p>Seasons, tides and the calmest hours of the day.</p><span class="tag">Coming soon</span></div></span>
<span class="gcard soon"><img src="/img/village-600.webp" alt="Road to Mont-Saint-Michel" loading="lazy"><div class="b"><h3>How to Get There</h3><p>By car, train and from Paris — the practical routes.</p><span class="tag">Coming soon</span></div></span>
</div>

<div class="gcat">The island &amp; its story</div>
<div class="gcards">
<span class="gcard soon"><img src="/img/ramparts-800.webp" alt="Tides around Mont-Saint-Michel" loading="lazy"><div class="b"><h3>The Tides</h3><p>When the sea surrounds the abbey, and how to watch it safely.</p><span class="tag">Coming soon</span></div></span>
<span class="gcard soon"><img src="/img/prison-800.webp" alt="History of Mont-Saint-Michel" loading="lazy"><div class="b"><h3>The History</h3><p>From an archangel's vision to abbey, prison and UNESCO site.</p><span class="tag">Coming soon</span></div></span>
<span class="gcard soon"><img src="/img/merveille-800.webp" alt="Architecture of Mont-Saint-Michel" loading="lazy"><div class="b"><h3>Architecture, Explained</h3><p>La Merveille, the cloister and how they built it on a rock.</p><span class="tag">Coming soon</span></div></span>
</div>
</div></main>

<footer><div class="wrap">
